6 at Valmontone.

727
00:39:25.446 --> 00:39:27.282
Those were the
orders he was given.

728
00:39:28.449 --> 00:39:31.035
- But Clark decides to
make a swift left turn.

729
00:39:31.035 --> 00:39:32.954
